  <div id="carouselWrapper" class="col-md-12 position-relative px-0">
    <div id="mainIndicators" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
      <ol class="carousel-indicators">
        <li data-target="#mainIndicators" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
        <li data-target="#mainIndicators" data-slide-to="1"></li>
        <li data-target="#mainIndicators" data-slide-to="2"></li>
      </ol>
      <div class="carousel-inner">
        <div class="carousel-item active">
          <img class="d-block w-100 mx-auto" src="/nmns/img/portfolio/cabin.png" alt="노쇼 전적 공유">
          <div class="carousel-caption col-8 col-md-7 text-center text-md-left">
            <h3>노쇼 전적 공유</h3>
            <p>앱 설치 없이 카카오톡으로<br class="d-lg-none"/> 간편하게 노쇼 전적을 신고, 공유합니다.</p>
            <p>우리 가게 뿐만 아니라 다른 가게에서<br class="d-lg-none"/> 공유한 노쇼 전적도 확인할 수 있어요!</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
          <img class="d-block w-100 mx-auto" src="/nmns/img/portfolio/cake.png" alt="예약관리">
          <div class="carousel-caption col-8 col-md-7 text-center text-md-left">
            <h3>예약관리</h3>
            <p>앱 설치 없이 카카오톡으로<br class="d-lg-none"/> 간편하게 예약을 추가합니다.</p>
            <p>예약한 고객 전화번호를 넣으면<br class="d-lg-none"/> 예약내용을 카카오톡으로 보내드려요.</p>
            <p>장소와 관계없이 웹페이지 접속만으로<br class="d-lg-none"/> 보다 상세하게 예약을 관리할 수 있어요!</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
          <img class="d-block w-100 mx-auto" src="/nmns/img/portfolio/circus.png" alt="간편한 예약취소">
          <div class="carousel-caption col-8 col-md-7 text-center text-md-left">
            <h3>간편한 예약취소</h3>
            <p>고객이 따로 연락하지 않아도<br class="d-lg-none"/> 카카오톡 버튼만 누르면 예약취소를 할 수 있어요!</p>
            <p>고객이 예약을 취소하면 점주님께 <br class="d-lg-none"/>예약취소 알림을 보내드립니다 :)</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#mainIndicators" role="button" data-slide="prev">
        <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="sr-only">이전</span>
      </a>
      <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#mainIndicators" role="button" data-slide="next">
        <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="sr-only">다음</span>
      </a>
    </div>
    <div class="loginPage col-sm-8 col-md-5 hide-sm">
      <div class="form mx-auto">
        <form id="signupForm" class=(input.type==="signin" && "hide") method="post" action="/signup">
          <div class="form-group">
            <input type="email" name="email" class="form-control" placeholder="nomore@noshow.com" value="${input.email}"/>
            <input id="signupPassword" type="password" name="password" class="form-control" placeholder="비밀번호"/>
            <input type="password" name="passwordRepeat" class="form-control" placeholder="비밀번호 확인"/>
            <button id="signupBtn" class="btn-primary">회원가입</button>
            <p class="message text-danger" if(input.type === "signup" && input.message)>${input.message}</p>
            <p class=["message", "text-secondary", (input.type === "signup" && input.message && "mt-1")]>계정이 있으신가요?<br class="d-lg-none d-md-inline-block d-sm-none"/> <a href="#" class="text-primary switchForm">로그인</a>해주세요.</p>
          </div>
        </form>
        <form id="signinForm" class=(input.type!=="signin" && "hide") method="post" action="/signin">
          <div class="form-group">
            <input type="email" name="email" class="form-control" placeholder="nomore@noshow.com" value="${input.email}"/>
            <input type="password" name="password" class="form-control" placeholder="비밀번호"/>
            <div class="form-check text-left">
              <input type="checkbox" class="form-check-input" id="rememberMeCheck" name="rememberMe" value="true" checked="checked"/>
              <label for="rememberMeCheck"></label>
              <label class="form-check-label align-text-top mb-3" for="rememberMeCheck">자동 로그인</label>
            </div>
            <button id="signinBtn" class="btn-primary">로그인</button>
            <p class="message text-danger" if(input.type === "signin" && input.message)>${input.message}</p>
            <p class=["message", "text-secondary", (input.type === "signin" && input.message && "mt-1")]>아직 계정이 없으신가요?<br class="d-lg-none d-md-inline-block d-sm-none"/> <a href="#" class="text-primary switchForm">간편하게 가입</a>해보세요.</p>
            <p class="message mt-1"><a class="passwordReset text-primary" href="#">비밀번호를 잊으셨나요?</a></p>
          </div>
        </form>
        <form id="resetForm" class="hide" method="post" action="/resetPassword">
          <div class="form-group">
            <input type="email" name="email" class="form-control" placeholder="nomore@noshow.com" value="${input.email}"/>
            <button id="resetBtn" class="btn-primary">비밀번호 재설정</button>
            <p class="message">비밀번호를 찾으셨다면<br class="d-lg-none d-md-inline-block d-sm-none"/><a class="returnSignin text-primary" href="#"> 다시 로그인</a>해주세요.</p>
          </div>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

